 help"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-5 space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-neutral-600","children":[[["$","p","0",{"children":"At Naptec we understand that it is important you take a break from time to time, which is where our respite care at home service can help."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"You do not have to shoulder all the care responsibilities alone. Our caregivers can help care for your loved one whilst you have a well-deserved break and are able to keep an appointment, enjoy a holiday or attend a special occasion. It is important to look after your own well-being too, and with our respite care service you can be confident that your loved one is safe, happy and well cared for at home."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"The regular demands of caring can lead to feelings of exhaustion, so it is important to recognise when you need a break. Taking a rest from caring by using a respite service means taking care of your health and wellbeing so you can continue to care."}],["$","p","3",{"children":"Our respite care service is beneficial in many ways:"}]],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc space-y-2 pl-5","children":[["$","li","Your loved one can stay at home whilst you take a break",{"children":"Your loved one can stay at home whilst you take a break"}],["$","li","It gives you peace of mind that your loved one is being cared for at home",{"children":"It gives you peace of mind that your loved one is being cared for at home"}],["$","li","It is tailored to your loved one's needs",{"children":"It is tailored to your loved one's needs"}],["$","li","You are able to take a rest from caring",{"children":"You are able to take a rest from caring"}],["$","li","It is delivered by caregivers matched to you and your loved one",{"children":"It is delivered by caregivers matched to you and your loved one"}],["$","li","It is given by highly trained and experienced caregivers",{"children":"It is given by highly trained and experienced caregivers"}]]}],null,null]}]]}],"$L3"